column16: Nick Swisher walks.    Alex Rodriguez to 3rd.    Robinson Cano to 2nd.
Robinson Cano singles on a ground ball to center fielder Ryan Kalish.    Brett Gardner scores.    Alex Rodriguez to 2nd.
Curtis Granderson pops out to third baseman Yamaico Navarro.
Derek Jeter singles on a ground ball to third baseman Yamaico Navarro.  Ramiro Pena advances to 3rd, on throwing error by third baseman Yamaico Navarro.
Ramiro Pena singles on a line drive to right fielder Bill Hall.
Brett Gardner called out on strikes.
Juan Pierre flies out to left fielder Bill Hall.
Brent Lillibridge grounds out, shortstop Jed Lowrie to first baseman Lars Anderson.    Brent Morel to 3rd.
Alejandro De Aza grounds out, second baseman Felipe Lopez to first baseman Lars Anderson.    Brent Morel to 2nd.
Brent Morel singles on a line drive to left fielder Bill Hall.
Omar Vizquel grounds out, third baseman Adrian Beltre to first baseman Victor Martinez.
Juan Pierre grounds into a force out, second baseman Felipe Lopez to shortstop Jed Lowrie.    Alexei Ramirez to 3rd.    Brent Morel out at 2nd.    Juan Pierre to 1st.
Brent Morel singles on a ground ball to left fielder Josh Reddick.    Carlos Quentin scores.    Alexei Ramirez to 2nd.
Andruw Jones pops out to second baseman Felipe Lopez.
John McDonald flies out to left fielder Bill Hall.
Lyle Overbay called out on strikes.
Casey Kotchman grounds out, second baseman Marco Scutaro to first baseman Victor Martinez.
